    <item>
      <title>纽约、加州成为美国众议院“僵局”的主要推动者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/new-york-california-loom-large-in-dead-heat-race-for-us-house</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州和加利福尼亚州在总统选举中经常被忽视，但它们正逐渐成为争夺美国众议院控制权的激烈斗争中的潜在关键战场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/new-york-california-loom-large-in-dead-heat-race-for-us-house</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗支持停火，以色列袭击更多真主党目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/israel-stages-massive-beirut-strikes-targeting-hezbollah-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列在贝鲁特郊区实施了大规模轰炸，并对黎巴嫩南部发动了地面袭击，而伊朗则表示将支持其盟友真主党和哈马斯之间的有条件停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/israel-stages-massive-beirut-strikes-targeting-hezbollah-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 06:55:38 GMT</pubDate>
